Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.04,0:24:36.44,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,There's a baby koala in the eucalyptus tree
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:41.07,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Looking for its mother from branch to branch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.34,0:24:45.78,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It gathers plenty of leaves to eat
